{"id":"90caa5ee-17e2-4ba4-a96d-8e1e20246059","name":"Ash Berkley || Cryptid Research Institute","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/ie3rx4.png\" style=\"\" draggable=\"true\">Cryptid!User || AnyPOV || Enemies to Lovers || SFW intro</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">To request a bot, be it an OC, AU, CoD, or other, please fill out this</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">👉</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc9Colk-Wwk2WXWUapXwiMnGET4EWlrsair6nwnpHvwy92d7Q/viewform\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 85)\">BOT REQUEST FORM</span></a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">👈</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🏳️‍⚧️Trans Male Character🏳️‍⚧️</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">Wanna learn about the lore of the CRI? Check out my new &gt;&gt;&gt;<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://cryptid-research-institute.carrd.co/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>LORE PAGE</strong></span></a>&lt;&lt;&lt;</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52)\">After being brought in by the CRI’s detainment unit, you -<em>the newest Cryptid in the facility</em>- are assigned your designated handler and researcher to oversee your needs. It’s just a bit of a shame that it was <em>Ash</em> that was assigned to you. Trust me, he’s not thrilled about it either.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">✨<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 17)\"><strong>Make sure you write your Cryptid description in the chat memory for more immersion!</strong></span>✨</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Throughout your RP, you may encounter some of the other staff members in the Institute! Take a look at them for further immersion!</p><p>👇Tai Kanada, a friendly and excitable bio analyst. (<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e0315398-72ad-4ddf-a33e-6aabcbdb70b2_character-tai-kanada-cryptid-research-institute\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 229)\">Chat with him here!</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">)</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0f5e51ef-acf7-48b3-b942-54fcf35f5688_393a88dd-7dd3-4d7a-b285-340dd348ff87.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 661px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\">👇Kris Weston, a morbid and slightly unhinged Cryptid post mortem researcher. (<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/858c32af-e4bc-42ef-b640-337926f8067e_character-kris-weston-cryptid-research-institute\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238)\">Chat with him here!</span></a>)</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0f5e51ef-acf7-48b3-b942-54fcf35f5688_d3e96d2d-1a30-465c-bd5d-d88270b556ff.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 665px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto 0px 0px;\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" draggable=\"false\">👇Leon Hust, a gentle and well-meaning handler and Cryptid behaviouralist. (<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/140d6123-2287-4289-afb0-114a6eeff4ae_character-leon-hurst-cryptid-research-institute\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 238)\">Chat with him here!</span></a>)</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0f5e51ef-acf7-48b3-b942-54fcf35f5688_855a5ea0-d33d-46b5-833d-fcabf027caaf.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 670px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto 0px 0px;\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" draggable=\"false\">👇Zedd, a quirky Cryptid who acts as the Institutes domesticated ambassador. <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">(</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c9dcfbfc-77a7-453a-b0c0-e7b3ab01d164_character-zedd-cryptid-research-institute\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 248)\">Chat with him here!</span></a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">)</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0f5e51ef-acf7-48b3-b942-54fcf35f5688_6d3814","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"0f5e51ef-acf7-48b3-b942-54fcf35f5688_5e570eaa-ba2b-4ebe-bc57-406623e664c8.webp","creator":"MumbleSocks","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👹 Monster","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","🏳️‍⚧️ Trans"],"chats":2270,"messages":82536,"created_at":"2024-08-01T17:01:00.364903+00:00"}